data.description: For buyers looking to step into the real estate market, look no further than 1213 1st Street, in the Midtown neighborhood of Key West. This could be your opportunity! This spacious two bedroom and one bathroom home sits on a huge 3,700 square foot lot. Features of the property include large, polished tiled flooring, a spacious and welcoming living room that joins up a designated dining area, and an updated galley-style kitchen with stone countertops and stainless steel appliances -- perfect for cooking up a favorite meal. Additional features include on-demand hot water and mini-split A/C units. This home is conveniently located in the center of Key West, just across the street from the Garrison Bight Marina, and within walking distance to Key West High School and Horace O'Bryant Elementary School. Shopping and transportation is also nearby. Buyers need to qualify under Workforce Housing Ordinance and Key West Income Guidelines. Call or text today for a private showing.
